chunks.lyrics: It's not too easy to find this song tabbed out, and when you do, it's
usually junk, so here you go. It's a pretty rough song to tab since
everything changes so quickly, but here it is, from start to finish,
the entire song. As usual I have the lyrics at the bottom but I didn't
place the chord changes above them like usual, since this song moves
so fast. So you'll just have to memorize it first.
I think, I think I know it all,
But can I be sure of the things I've grown to know about
And can I say I know it all,
When rules just guide me to blindly follow
or just the fucked up dreams
I think, I think I know it all
But is our beliefs just stringing us along
And was there something wrong in what
I heard for every hour of the day?
or just the fucked up dreams
I think, I think I know it all
I think, I think I know it all
or just the fucked up dreams
